[SHORT DESC]
If it misses, user loses HP equal to 1/2 the damage that would have been dealt.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>If Hi Jump Kick misses or the target uses Protect or Detect, the user loses HP equal to 1/2 the damage it would have dealt if it had hit. If Hi Jump Kick targets a Ghost-type Pok√©mon, the user loses HP equal to 1/2 the damage that would have been dealt had the target not been a Ghost-type. The damage caused by Hi Jump Kick missing is capped at 1/2 the target's max HP.</p>